this projet name morpion is a little game which played enter two terminals.

Exemple using :
./morpion
my_pid: 12345
waiting for enemy connection...

./morpion 12345
my_pid: 6789
successfully connected

if the 1st player has connected he display : enemy connected

after, the game begining and is at the 1st player to play


